{"tid":542512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"KOL Hello Pinkey周圍食收錢幫犯法BBQ場賣廣告","createTime":"2018-01-27T14:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T03:45:21.000Z","uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aae6bfadd15d59a0916e4a64bf6e7afd1b4538e1","tid":542512,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:12:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">KOL為左錢咩都做得出 特別係呢個女人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n次次介紹d野都好撚伏 on99今次仲幫人犯法賣廣告<br />\n點先可以推到單野個個都知？唔好去食<br />\n<br />\n「事源Hello Pinkey近日在facebook page大力宣傳天水圍靚環境BBQ，盛讚該燒烤場設計浪費適合情侶，加上食材質素比大多任食場佳，老闆又很大方容許大家自己在外面買料帶進來燒烤，亦有娛樂設施，讚到「天上有，地下無」。最後表明目的，呼籲大家讚好、分享post、tag朋友，將會抽出10個幸運兒送出優惠入場券，由原價$1824(八人用），減到$1600(八人用），足足節省了$224，相等於一人$28。<br />\n<br />\n可是蘋果日報早就於2016年揭發天水圍嘉湖山莊旁有座泥頭山，事隔兩年泥頭山已改建成燒烤場牟利，涉及違契違規問題。議員及網民批評即使收錢也不應推介泥頭山，一來危險，二來很多灰塵、垃圾，很大機會令食客肚痛收場。如果有職業道德應該盡早查清楚燒烤場的背景，免生事端。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.fanpiece.com/m/purestalker/c1308623.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.fanpiece.com%2Fm%2Fpurestalker%2Fc1308623.html&d=KTvhzHJOOhPbuCDzUM1TXfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ea72998b\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.fanpiece.com/m/purestalker/c1308623.html</a>"},{"pid":"3b8c017ab4b007855355d8397f18b2fc13e4ac26","tid":542512,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hellopinkey/videos/10155198619446845/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhellopinkey%2Fvideos%2F10155198619446845%2F&d=KTvhzHJOOhPbuCDzUM1TXfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c73a82ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hellopinkey/videos/10155198619446845/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推爆佢個post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ef8e2f0a32f65b98e8401d7b3a83ed44ca53c7","tid":542512,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}